&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;废话不多说,先展示下我写博客时的样子&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img src= &#34;https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/img/loading.svg&#34; data-lazy-src=&#34;https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/blog/GVmwUQ.png&#34; alt=&#34;20210302220625&#34; /&gt;
